sequenceDiagram
    actor S as Student
    participant FE as Frontend React
    participant MW as Auth Middleware
    participant RC as Resume Controller
    participant ENG as Analysis Engine
    participant DB as MongoDB
    S->>FE: Upload PDF + Select Experience Level
    FE->>MW: POST /api/v1/resume/analyze JWT + File
    MW->>MW: Verify JWT via Clerk SDK
    MW->>RC: Forward Request with userId
    RC->>RC: Extract text from PDF
    RC->>ENG: extractSkillsFromText
    RC->>DB: Fetch all JobRoles
    RC->>ENG: calculateResumeScore
    RC->>ENG: matchSkills extracted vs required
    RC->>DB: Fetch IndustryTrends
    RC->>ENG: recommendRoles
    RC->>ENG: generateAIFeedback
    RC->>ENG: generateImprovementPlan
    RC->>DB: ResumeAnalysis.create all results
    RC->>DB: getUserRank
    DB-->>RC: Rank Info
    RC-->>FE: JSON Response score feedback plan rank
    FE-->>S: Display Analysis Result Page
